OL,3,CCritical incident remains in place at
OL,4,Chospital following heatwave
OL,6,FA critical incident remains in place
OL,7,Fat University Hospital Southampton
OL,8,Fafter it declared its "hospitals are
OL,9,Fcurrently full".
OL,11,FThe critical status was first declared
OL,12,Fon Thursday (25 June) during the
OL,13,Fheatwave, which the hospital says
OL,14,Fplaced significant pressure on its
OL,15,Fservices.
OL,17,FThe Trust says the hospital is
OL,18,Fcontinuing to care for a "significant
OL,19,Fnumber" of people who became unwell
OL,20,Fduring the recent hot weather.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
