OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1782737333
OL,3,CCritical incident remains in place at
OL,4,Chospital following heatwave
OL,6,FWaiting times at the Emergency
OL,7,FDepartment are currently up to 12
OL,8,Fhours, with very high demand for
OL,9,Fmedical care continuing.
OL,11,FThe Trust says its clinical teams are
OL,12,F"actively turning away" people whose
OL,13,Fconditions could be treated elsewhere.
OL,15,FIn a statement, University Hospital
OL,16,FSouthampton said: "We ask for your
OL,17,Fpatience and kindness as our staff
OL,18,Fwork incredibly hard under intense
OL,19,Fpressure.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
