OL,3,CCritical incident remains in place at
OL,4,Chospital following heatwave
OL,6,F"Aggression and abuse towards our
OL,7,Fstaff is not acceptable and will not
OL,8,Fbe tolerated.
OL,10,F"Thank you for your ongoing
OL,11,Funderstanding and support."
